17
00:01:02,395 --> 00:01:05,565
{\an8}<i>Days of realizing those passions
has now begun.</i>

18
00:01:29,089 --> 00:01:32,092
<i>This is documentary series</i> RIDE ON TIME.

19
00:01:34,494 --> 00:01:39,265
<i>TOKIO Inc.'s first project
began to turn its gears in April.</i>

20
00:01:40,567 --> 00:01:43,670
Good morning.

21
00:01:44,671 --> 00:01:46,706
I'm Joshima, the president.
Nice to meet you.

22
00:01:46,773 --> 00:01:47,807
Wow...

23
00:01:48,408 --> 00:01:51,144
<i>Creating things is
one of the company's philosophies.</i>

24
00:01:52,345 --> 00:01:53,713
<i>Their first job is</i>

25
00:01:53,780 --> 00:01:58,685
<i>teaming up with a national udon chain
to create new menu items.</i>

26
00:01:59,986 --> 00:02:01,654
