27
00:02:02,155 --> 00:02:02,989
Thank you.

28
00:02:04,124 --> 00:02:07,760
<i>TOKIO Inc. developed ideas such as this.</i>

29
00:02:09,262 --> 00:02:13,867
As a parent, I'd want to put something
with more color in their meal.

30
00:02:14,767 --> 00:02:17,537
<i>It's an udon meal for children.</i>

31
00:02:22,108 --> 00:02:25,612
<i>After much trial and error at home,
Matsuoka makes a new menu item,</i>

32
00:02:28,848 --> 00:02:31,885
<i>curry udon that has tomatoes and eggs.</i>

33
00:02:35,755 --> 00:02:37,657
This is the menu for summer this year.

34
00:02:38,791 --> 00:02:40,193
I'm so happy to hear that.

35
00:02:41,828 --> 00:02:45,798
<i>They're part of the whole process,
from beginning to end.</i>

36
00:02:45,865 --> 00:02:46,699
Yeah.

37
00:02:47,901 --> 00:02:51,337
<i>This is how TOKIO Inc. gets things done.</i>

38
