accidentally bumped into this.

69
00:04:42,782 --> 00:04:44,150
Like, "Cut that out!"

70
00:04:46,686 --> 00:04:48,288
-Good morning.
-Good morning.

71
00:04:48,354 --> 00:04:49,389
Morning.

72
00:04:50,957 --> 00:04:51,991
Any without cracks?

73
